OL,3,CWind and rain causes disruption around
OL,4,Cthe region
OL,6,FHeavy rainfall and strong winds have
OL,7,Fbeen causing disruption to our region,
OL,8,Fwith the Met Office warning that this
OL,9,Fmay continue into tomorrow.
OL,11,FIn the early hours of 9 April 2024,
OL,12,Fthe coastguard requested the launch of
OL,13,FStranraer inshore lifeboat (ILB) to
OL,14,Fassist a sailing vessel who's anchor
OL,15,Fhad slipped and was drifting near to
OL,16,FWig Bay in Loch Ryan.
OL,18,FWith poor and difficult weather
OL,19,Fconditions Stranraer ILB launched and
OL,20,Fquickly found the vessel with two
OL,21,Fpeople onboard.
