OL,6,FThe vessel was towed to safe water and
OL,7,Fthen to Stranraer Marina where they
OL,8,Fwere met by the Stranraer Coastguard
OL,9,Fand Ballantrae Coastguard.
OL,11,FNot long after, a second vessel was
OL,12,Fthen seen entering the marina,
OL,13,Fstruggling with the poor weather
OL,14,Fconditions and the Stranraer ILB and
OL,15,Fcoastguard teams were dispatched to
OL,16,Fassist the vessel.
