OL,6,FIn a Facebook post, operations manager
OL,7,FSean Hannah stated: "Howling winds and
OL,8,Fwaves are difficult enough conditions,
OL,9,Fbut when launching to a casualty at
OL,10,Fsea, that adds even more difficulty,
OL,11,Fstress and danger.
OL,13,F"A strong wind was barrelling down the
OL,14,FLoch with a confused sea state, it was
OL,15,Fa continuous battle throughout, the
OL,16,Fcrew and coastguard teams carried out
OL,17,Fthe service in a tremendous manner,
OL,18,Fbringing two vessels and their crew to
OL,19,Fsafety.
