OL,6,F"It's thanks to your kindness that
OL,7,Fcrews like Stranraer RNLI are able to
OL,8,Fface all that the sea can throw at
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,F"Without your support, they wouldn't
OL,12,Fhave the kit, training and incredible
OL,13,Fboats that can tackle storms like this
OL,14,F- thank you."
