OL,6,FIn other parts of the region, the
OL,7,FWhitesands Riverside Car Park was
OL,8,Fclosed and people were asked to remove
OL,9,Ftheir vehicles, following a SEPA flood
OL,10,Fwarning, stating the Nith could enter
OL,11,Fthe car park this afternoon.
OL,13,FSEPA still has flood warnings in place
OL,14,Ffor the Nith Tidal and Eyemouth
OL,15,FCoastal areas.
